overview: On April 30th GCW presents In Too Deep live on FITE straight from Showboat in Atlantic City. The event features the GCW Tag Titles match - Bussy vs Briscoes vs Second Gear Crew.  Also in the lineup:  Joey Janela vs Bailey  Chris Dickinson vs Biff Slater  JWM vs Cole Radrick  Akira vs Hoodfoot  Spencer Slade vs Wreck  Jordan Oliver vs Masha Slamovic  .... and more!
title: GCW In Too Deep
